       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ACCOUNT-BALANCE-PROG.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  ACCOUNT-BALANCE        PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 1000.00.
       01  DEPOSIT-AMOUNT         PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 250.00.
       01  WITHDRAWAL-AMOUNT      PIC 9(4)V99 VALUE 100.00.
       01  AMOUNT-FMT             PIC Z(4).99.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "Initial Balance : " ACCOUNT-BALANCE.

           MOVE DEPOSIT-AMOUNT TO AMOUNT-FMT.
           DISPLAY "Deposited       : " AMOUNT-FMT.

           MOVE WITHDRAWAL-AMOUNT TO AMOUNT-FMT.
           DISPLAY "Withdrawn       : " AMOUNT-FMT.

           ADD DEPOSIT-AMOUNT TO ACCOUNT-BALANCE.
           SUBTRACT WITHDRAWAL-AMOUNT FROM ACCOUNT-BALANCE.
           MOVE ACCOUNT-BALANCE TO AMOUNT-FMT.
           DISPLAY "Final Balance   : " AMOUNT-FMT.

           IF 1 = 2
               DISPLAY ACCOUNT-BALANCE
           END-IF.

           STOP RUN.


